attr.title: Watch Ducks Legacy
attr.desc: Something new to do between playing your favourite ports -- watch ducks and collect points that build with every session.
attr.inst: Download from itch.io (https://jdmgames.itch.io/watch-ducks-legacy), extract, and place *Watch Ducks Legacy.exe* in watchduckslegacy/assets
attr.inst_md: Download from [itch.io](https://jdmgames.itch.io/watch-ducks-legacy), extract, and place `Watch Ducks Legacy.exe` in `watchduckslegacy/assets`
